Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:49.54,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(1076,380)}能够和你一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:49.54,Notice,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(1026,462)}是我的骄傲
